505593,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T00:28:24.000Z","msg":"遼寧號航母編隊在台灣以東的菲律賓海向宮古海峽前進。從南海出發開始就一直插在編隊中尾隨&ldquo;護衛&rdquo;遼寧艦的美軍阿利伯克級驅逐艦（位置6）還在編隊中。綜合補給艦&ldquo;呼倫湖&rdquo;還是遠遠落在美驅逐艦後面。原來，阿利伯克級是請來護衛的&ldquo;外援&rdquo;哦！會不會一直把遼寧號送到家啊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BoDiplo/status/1386675918983270401?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBoDiplo%2Fstatus%2F1386675918983270401%3Fs%3D20&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=24c299c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBoDiplo%2Fstatus%2F1386675918983270401%3Fs%3D20&h=6b9ab1d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BoDiplo/status/1386675918983270401?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"5095c2bcfda2fa283c41938458c8653deaf9bc23","tid":2505593,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T00:30:38.000Z","msg":"在目視距離內監控共軍遼寧號航母編隊，在網路引發熱議；後來傳出還有日本自衛隊艦艇也在附近監控。<br />\n<br />\n動物園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a0249b3f1f49a9a4c26e1d12e0c20730126b4e","tid":2505593,"uid":391165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T00:31:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYcLnuwaz32pCoSiwZsW7qfPvv1fSv7bSRweuKpUP4wGq?filename=5YoTFE8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YoTFE8.jpg&h=37fc8720&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed14aa5cf0b19f9447e143298f5d3db865e2b2dc","tid":2505593,"uid":94480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T00:36:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BwN5tuW0Evs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBwN5tuW0Evs&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=c83bca56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BwN5tuW0Evs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"h